outputs.output_descr: The objective of this project is to assist the Government of Timor-Leste (GoTL) to conduct a comprehensive assessment of the existing information on biodiversity in Timor-Leste, prepare its National Report to the UNCBD COP, prepare NBSAP and establsihment of an operational Clearing House Mechanism (CHM)

project_descr: PIMS 4083:  National Biodiversity Strategy and Action Plan and related Enabling Activities in Timor-Leste
project_title: National Biodiversity Startegy and Action Plan (NBSAP)
